basic_info.description: Im Caelin Hargrave.I recently finished a 8 year commitment to the Navy where I served as an aviation electronics technician. Before joining the military I attended Texas Tech university to get a bachelor's degree in computer science. After a few years I decided to join the military for a break and to get my college paid for. Now I'm just trying to reach that same end goal on a way shorter time frame. My goal is to work in the WEB 3 space to makenew things that change the way we interact on the internet.
